message: Miami, Florida, The Miami-Dade State Attorney’s Office hosts the National Human Trafficking Prosecution Summit in partnership with the Association of Prosecuting Attorneys (APA) and the University of Miami.

data.description: The Miami-Dade State Attorney’s Office hosts the National Human Trafficking Prosecution Summit on January 7 at the University of Miami.
